Package: XOMultinom
Type: Package
Title: Exact distributions of some functions of the ordered multinomial counts
Version: 0.6.3
Date: 2025-03-01
Authors@R: c(
  person("Sergio", "Venturini", role=c("aut", "cre"), email = "sergio.venturini@unicatt.it"),
  person("Marco", "Bonetti", role=c("ctb"), email = "marco.bonetti@unibocconi.it"))
Description: Functions that implements the exact algorithms to compute the distribution
    of the maximum, the minimum, the range and the sum of the J largest order statistics
    of a multinomial random vector under the hypothesis of equiprobability
    (<http://dx.doi.org/10.1098/rsos.190198>).
Maintainer: Sergio Venturini <sergio.venturini@unicatt.it>
License: GPL-3
